import "./App.css"
import Navbar from "./common/Navbar/Navbar"
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route, Link } from "react-router-dom"

function App() {
  return (
    <>
      <Navbar/>
      <Router>
        <Navbar />
        <Switch>
          <Route path='/'></Route>
        </Switch>
      </Router>
    </>
  )
}

export default App
